data.description: Stunning home site, offering privacy and tranquility. This property is loaded with impressive features and details. The kitchen boasts beautiful granite counters, ample cabinetry making meal prep a breeze. The open floor plan flows seamlessly from the kitchen into the dining area and great room. The main level includes owner's suite is a true retreat on its own wing, with plenty of space for a king-sized bed and a sitting area. 2 additional bedrooms are well-sized and shared bath. The upstairs provides additional living space and is perfect for a playroom/media room or sleeping quarters. Two-car garage, main lvl covered back porch/patio; this home is an excellent choice for those seeking a comfortable, convenient lifestyle.
